# ADK local runtime cache (per-app session/state) — must never ship in the Cloud Run
# image. `.gcloudignore` does `#!include:.gitignore`, so listing it here also keeps a
# `gcloud run deploy --source .` build context clean (e.g. agent_apps/<app>/.adk/).
.adk/
